rows.label: xs33660100_MSG0010
rows.name: It is a stroke of luck that we should meet here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33660100_MSG0020
rows.name:
Attend. I have been scouting the surroundings
for a way to approach our foe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33660100_MSG0030
rows.name:
Void has command of the Ganglion...
That wretch ground Wrothian honor into dust.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33660100_MSG0040
rows.name: Fear not. I dare not try to slay him alone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33660100_MSG0050
rows.name:
Now, with valued allies,
we bring our joint might to bear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33660100_MSG0060
rows.name:
Come, our goals are aligned.
Let us venture forth![ST:wait ]
